- Using * MongoDB * as a Document Database
- Using * Docker compose * for make development easy to dev
- Using * Makefile * as a Buildtool
- Using * github.com/go-playground/validator/v10 * as a struct validation
- Using * github.com/caarlos0/env/v11 * as a env parser and validator
- Using * https://github.com/aidantwoods/go-paseto * as a token generator and parser
- Using * Bruno * as a http client and API specs documents

